PeopleSoft version 1.01
=======================

This set of modules provides functions which facilitate work with
PeopleSoft's ERP applications.

The modules are:

	o PeopleSoft		Overall documentation and generic 
				functions.

	o PeopleSoft::Tools	SQR profiler

	o PeopleSoft::EPM	Functions to administer EPM

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

These modules were developed using PeopleTools version 8.1x and 8.4x.
The environment uses Oracle and a few of the functions use Oracle's
system tables and will have to be modified to work with a different
DBMS.

